Nɛrɛ ye sahɛli jamana yiri madonnen ye. Nafa caman bɛ sɔrɔ nɛrɛ la. Misali la, a mugu bɛ don, a kolo bɛ kɛ sunbala ye. Sunbalaji bɛ dilan ni sunbala ye. Sunbalaji makadi kosobɛ Mali kɔnɔ. O de kɔsɔn, najini dilannaw ye najini dɔ dilana k'o tɔgɔ wele sunbalani. Kɛnɛyatigilamaw y'a sɛminciya, sɛgɛsɛgɛli caman kɔnɔfɛ, k'a jɔyɔrɔ ka bon hali kɛnɛya sabati la. Sanko joli cayabana bɛ mɔgɔ minu la ani bugu dalen don minu ɲana yeli la.
